{"tid":1379870,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢幫左韓國人","createTime":"2019-07-29T01:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T12:58:34.000Z","uid":70565,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bc866e1c700671a9bca25c7babd1e09c028072b4","tid":1379870,"uid":70565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:09:12.000Z","msg":"琴日發夢喺中環有一班韓國人 唔知咩事唔知點走 小弟本身識韓文 所以教佢地點行番去地鐵站之後同佢地講香港發生咩事 冇幾耐送左佢地去地鐵站之後就見到另一對韓國夫妻 我見佢地都好似冇方向 所以又走上去幫手 佢地原來住ibis 我話順路阿 之後一齊行過去 話佢地知你住既地方好危險 但最危險既係警察 唔係示威者 佢地都好佩服香港人 希望我地盡早獨立 之後個夢就醒左了<br />\n<br />\n大家8月5號見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b394a8d978859820a79c90cadcdf20989c66768f","tid":1379870,"uid":70565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:13:34.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"d70891ba9cb8d0515faa0681e658ae19135c7ac5","tid":1379870,"uid":70565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:13:50.000Z","msg":"8月5號 全港罷工"},{"pid":"11872b63c9f4cd6406788d5a45737e084ad7b146","tid":1379870,"uid":265256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:15:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ac2f97e23caeeafeb5ef3e95c1eb0135d16d504f","tid":1379870,"uid":70565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:15:25.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"c38cbaa3e7ecd193c7313842ec21f0ab98836315","tid":1379870,"uid":70565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:39:36.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"b9a712b8c4f552b3a3796d7a3f308d73a0d6d2eb","tid":1379870,"uid":258300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T12:58:34.000Z","msg":"光復中國"}]}